Spool-dispatch gate marker set: prd.yml, mutables.yml, needs-gm, gm-fired-<sessionId>, residual-check-fired -- these are the on-disk marker files SpoolDispatcher's checkDispatchGates() reads to gate Write/Edit/git pre-execution, tracked via .gm/ not hook events. Skill(skill='gm') clears the needs-gm gate specifically; one shipped skill, no subagent variant of the gate-clearing mechanism.